### 5. [tests/journey_tests.rs](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/tests/journey_tests.rs) — Temporal Simulation Harness

#### [MODIFY] [journey_tests.rs](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/tests/journey_tests.rs)

New test: `test_journey_temporal_harness_usa_radicalization`

Per Management directive (RE: V16, §II):

```
1. Init USA archetype at (+1, 0). Overton center near (0, 0).
2. Run chronos.tick() × 10.
3. At tick 3: inject radical leftward policy (attempt shift to -2 on X-axis).
4. Assert tick 4: Authority drops, Ideological Tension spikes.
5. Assert tick 5-6: Rubber Band pull is active (position drifting back).
6. Assert tick 10: Either position has stabilized (AUT/STB paid) or Estate rebellion fired.
```

This is the capstone Journey Test for Phase 16 and the game's primary difficulty balance tool.

