## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```powershell
cargo test --manifest-path brinkmanship_engine/Cargo.toml
```

**New tests to add:**
- `test_rubber_band_gradual_pull` — verifies position drifts toward center over ticks, not teleports
- `test_rubber_band_authority_bleed` — verifies AUT drains per tick when outside spread
- `test_glacial_shift_slow_drift` — verifies position moves slowly from estate momentum
- `test_estate_velocity_shock` — verifies Capital Flight triggers on fast acceleration
- `test_perception_filter_veil_shatters` — verifies None returned beyond collapse threshold
- `test_journey_temporal_harness_usa_radicalization` — the 10-tick headless loop test

### Dependency Order
```
IdeologyComponent fields (state.rs)
    ├── Rubber Band + Glacial Shift (chronos.rs)  [IDX-006, IDX-007]
    ├── Estate Velocity Shock (chronos.rs)
    ├── Perception Filter cost (ideology_matrix.rs)
    └── Temporal Harness Test (journey_tests.rs)
ScenarioDef (scenario.rs)  [independent]
flavor_label UI wire (IdeologyCompass.tsx)  [independent]
```

